10398.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10398.description: When a volcanic vent under Goo Lagoon becomes active, a giant volatile gas bubble rises to the surface. Plankton manages to get his evil little hands on the bubble and threatens to pop it, covering all of Bikini Bottom in goo, unless Mr. Krabs gives him the Krabby Patty formula. It's up to SpongeBob, Patrick and Sandy to find a way to thwart Plankton and save the town

10399.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
10399.description: Sokka reviews the maps they acquired from the Spirit Library. After accidentally soaking the maps with a Waterbending bomb (similar to doing a cannonball in a pool), Katara uses her Waterbending to extract the water from the maps. The group then huddles around the map to discuss in which direction they should go – the Serpent's Pass appears to be the most direct route.

10400.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
10400.description: Aang discovers a secret Fire Nation super weapon heading straight for Ba Sing Se and must stop it before it destroys the great wall that protects the city from invasion. Meanwhile, Jet wishes to recruit Zuko for his Freedom Fighters, but learns a dangerous secret about him instead.

10401.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10401.description: SpongeBob is desperate to have Squidward visit him at home, but Squidward says there's no reason for him to come over, especially when he's perfectly comfortable in his own home. // All of SpongeBob's square pants have shrunk in the dryer. When he goes to the store to buy some more, he finds that the store is all out of square pants! With no other choice, SpongeBob decides to try a new look - round pants!

10402.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10402.description: Mermaidman and Barnacleboy are booked to attend a shuffleboarding tournament, but they can't go because they're laid up in the hospital. // When Squidward is mistaken for his much more famous rival, Squilliam Fancyson, he is invited to teach a class at the most prestigious music school in Bikini Bottom.

10403.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
10403.description: The Shredder kidnaps and experiments on the Mighty Mutanimals.

10404.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
10404.description: Mikey and Casey are befriended by Mondo Gecko, a radical skateboarding reptilian kid.

10405.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10405.description: When Shifu's con-man father comes back into town, Po finds himself in the middle.

10406.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10406.description: Po is excited when he discovers a kung fu prodigy, but starts to worry when people seem to prefer the new kid to their beloved Dragon Warrior.

10407.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10407.description: Marlene discovers a lost egg, and asks the penguins to care for it and keep it safe. But King Julien is jealous, and wants to raise the egg to be his second in command. // When Skipper steals the batteries to Julien’s stereo, he sets off a wild chase around the zoo that gets both of them stuck in the habitat of an angry kangaroo.

10408.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10408.description: The penguins compete against the lemurs in a game of capture the flag. This should be easy for the crack penguin team, but for some mysterious reason the lemurs keep beating them to the flag. // Mort is kicked out of the lemur habitat after he touches King Julien’s feet one too many times. So, the penguins take him in and attempt to break him of his foot obsession.

10409.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10409.description: After a freak bicycling accident, Squidward is coated in so much mud, leaves, and gunk to make him totally unrecognizable. The residents of Bikini Bottom think that Squidward is some sort of monster come to terrorize the town. // After practicing all day with his brand new magic kit, SpongeBob tries to impress Squidward with his newfound abilities. Of course Squidward, being the ever reluctant participant, sneaks away without SpongeBob noticing.

10410.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10410.description: SpongeBob has failed his driving test - again. Pat is so outraged by the injustice of it all that he storms into the testing facility and takes the test to prove that it is an unfair test and impossible to pass. // An oversight in a Royal genealogy document reveals that Patrick is the next in line to receive a kingly title. It's not long before the power of the crown goes straight to the starfish's head.

10411.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10411.description: SpongeBob's favorite jellyfishing net is missing! And worst of all, Pat may have been the one that stole it. // Rejected yet again by Squidward, SpongeBob decides that if he can't hang with the real Squid, he'll make his own. So SpongeBob builds a ventriloquist dummy modeled after his favorite neighbor.

10412.title: Nella The Princess Knight
10412.description: Nella helps Cici learn how to stand up and stand out when Tricksy tries to steal a sparkly trophy. // Too big to fit on the fair rides, a giant ogre shrinks himself using a magical wishing wagon.

10413.title: Nella The Princess Knight
10413.description: Nella journeys to Riley's kingdom in search of a special glowfruit for King Dad's surprise birthday cake. // When Gork dresses as Nella for a costume party, a villain mistakes him for the real princess knight.

10414.title: Bubble Guppies
10414.description: With an "oink, oink" here and a "moo, moo" there, the Bubble Guppies learn all about farm animals ... and discover that a lot of their favorite foods come from a farm too!

10415.title: Bubble Guppies
10415.description: The play's the thing when the Bubble Guppies go to see a production of 'The Three Little Pigs.' But when one of the actors can't perform, it's up to Deema to put on the costume and take the stage.

10416.title: Dora the Explorer
10416.description: Boots can't wait for a super duper toy fire truck that's coming in the mail. But when the package arrives, the box is empty! Seems the toy fell out and is now sitting far away on top of Snowy Mountain.

10417.title: Dora the Explorer
10417.description: The stick, the stick, the Magic Stick! Dora and Boots find a magic stick and according to the wise old Tree Frog, it's up to our two young heroes to go to the top of the Highest Hill to make the stick do its magic trick.

10418.title: Rusty Rivets
10418.description: Liam wants to visit an amusement park, but obstacles in the way delay them from getting there in time, so Rusty makes a theme park just for him. // Rusty builds a big vacuum to clean up Liam's mess and find his screwdriver but the megavac starts to suck up too much!

10419.title: Rusty Rivets
10419.description: Rusty and Ruby turn Sammy Scoops into Captain Scoops, an ice cream superhero, in order to sell the most ice cream. // The kids find the courage to search for a mysterious mythical creature.

10420.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
10420.description: Blaze and his driver AJ are introduced to a world of racing Monster Machines. But when a truck named Crusher uses tricks to try and win the Championship Race, Blaze will do everything he can to help his friends and beat Crusher to the finish line.

10421.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
10421.description: Blaze and his driver AJ are introduced to a world of racing Monster Machines. But when a truck named Crusher uses dirty tricks to try and win the Championship Race, Blaze will do everything he can to help his friends and beat Crusher to the finish line.

10422.title: PAW Patrol
10422.description: Ryder and the PAW Patrol clean up a small oil spill in the water near Adventure Bay. They must plug the hole in the ship, clean up the oil and save the animals and fish in Adventure Bay./When Adventure Bay’s famous statue ends up at the bottom of the Bay, Ryder and the PAW Patrol have to help Mayor Goodway and find a clever way to bring it back!

10423.title: PAW Patrol
10423.description: It’s Adventure Bay Western Days. The whole town is enjoying the activities when a herd of cows escape from a train at the railway station. Now it’s like the real old west, with the PAW Patrol rounding up cows. Yeehaw!/When their friend Alex decides he wants to be a member of the PAW Patrol the PUPS and Ryder let him come along for the ride. Rescuing Cali the cat from farmer Yumi’s barn becomes more of a challenge when Alex tries to help!

10424.title: PAW Patrol
10424.description: Alex loses his back pack on the first day of school! Ryder and the Paw Patrol need to help him find it before the school bus comes./It’s Chase’s birthday and the pups are planning a surprise party. A storm causes the power to go out. The Paw Patrol have to fix the power and save Chases Birthday party.

10425.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10425.description: When Sandy goes out of town for a few days, she puts SpongeBob and Patrick in charge of her pet caterpillar. // Mr. Krabs keeps trying new sales gimmicks for the Krusty Krab, but none of them work. SpongeBob comes up with an idea for colored krabby patties, but Mr. Krabs scoffs at him reminding him to leave the creative thinking to him.

10426.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10426.description: When SpongeBob's grandma gives him a kiss in public, the guys at work tease him about being a little baby. // Squid is so sick and tired of living between SpongeBob and Pat that he decides to leave Bikini Bottom and go someplace where everyone is just like him.

10427.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10427.description: Sandy is going into hibernation in one week and she wants to pack a million activities for her and SpongeBob to do together in that short time. // Mr. Krabs tells SpongeBob and Pat that it's okay to borrow things as long as you put them back. So SpongeBob and Pat borrow a balloon from the Bargain Mart and they accidentally pop it.

10428.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10428.description: When Kowalski's ray designed to freshen spoiled food accidentally hits Skipper before falling down a storm drain, the leader is turned into a baby penguin, albeit retaining much of Skipper's adult personality. // After learning of Savio's escape from Hoboken on a TV news report, the penguins organize an effort to protect the zoo from the vengeful boa.

10429.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10429.description: Kowalski’s obsession with Doris the dolphin drives him to invent a love ray, the Love-U-Laser. It works like a charm until Alice falls for a trashcan, Julien falls for Mort, and Skipper orders the ray to be put in reverse. Private gets hit by the reverse ray and instantly loathes Kowalski. Matters get much worse as the loathe ray explodes and everybody hates Kowalski! He’s only got one shot to stop being the most loathed penguin in the world. // Told as a courtroom flashback, Kowalski unwisely revives Jiggles in a small, whipped cream-eating version. The little green cubes multiply on impact, however, and are soon threatening to cover the surface of the earth. As the Jiggli multiply out of control, will the team be able to prevent the jiggli-fication of the world?

10430.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10430.description: Po is distraught when he learns that everyone in town has been invited to a fancy dinner party except for him, due to his slovenly behavior and table manners. Will Shifu and the Five be able to teach Po proper etiquette AND foil the attack of evil Temutai and his army? Not likely.

10431.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10431.description: When Shifu's ex-girlfriend, Mei Ling, visits the Jade Palace, Po decides to try and get them back together, despite the fact Mei Ling is now Shifu's most hated enemy.

10432.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
10432.description: The Turtles get whisked through time by apprentice Time Master Renet, and they must all work together to defeat the evil Time Master Savanti Romero.

10433.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
10433.description: The Turtles are accidentally transported to the past, and they cross paths with a familiar ninja clan.

10434.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10434.description: Patrick invents a new board game, and invites SpongeBob, Sandy and Squidward to play it with him. // After accidentally flushing Mr. Krabs’ safe, SpongeBob and Squidward must go into the sewers to find it.

10435.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10435.description: SpongeBob gets a pair of long pants, but they change his life in unexpected ways. // When Larry the Lobster opens a new gym in Bikini Bottom, SpongeBob becomes his best customer.

10436.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10436.description: Sandy tries to study SpongeBob and Patrick’s behavior, but her science experiment goes horribly awry. // Mr. Krabs takes Plankton’s advice, and finally marries the only thing he ever loved…money!

10437.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10437.description: Po befriends a band of dancers, unaware they're actually a band of traveling thieves.

10438.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10438.description: When the Furious 5 are all out of town and the Jade Palace is attacked, Po only has his dad and two old people to help him.

10439.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10439.description: Marlene goes over to meet the newest zoo animal, and she mysteriously disappears. The penguins and lemurs attempt to rescue her, but they are taken, too. All except for Kowalski, the last penguin standing. // When Julien is taken to the zoo infirmary for acting even weirder than usual, Maurice is left in charge. Everything goes smoothly, until suddenly Maurice is acting even crazier than Julien ever did.

10440.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10440.description: The penguins and lemurs face off in a race. The penguins in a souped-up version of their car and the lemurs in Alice's zoo cart. Winner takes the loser's car! // Alice gives Rico a tummy-settling medicine just after he swallows a ticking time bomb.

10441.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
10441.description: Karai is brainwashed and starts hunting the Turtles.

10442.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
10442.description: The Turtles get whisked through time by apprentice Time Master Renet, and they must all work together to defeat the evil Time Master Savanti Romero.

10443.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10443.description: Mr. Krabs gets trapped in Bikini Bottom’s brand-new bank, and it’s up to SpongeBob & Patrick to save him. // After failing again to steal the Krabby Patty formula, Plankton gets a pet to cheer himself up.

10444.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10444.description: SpongeBob and Patrick go to see the latest horror film, only to be seemingly stalked by the villain. // SpongeBob holds a séance at the Krusty Krab to learn the recipe for a long-lost sandwich.

10445.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10445.description: SpongeBob will do anything to get to meet his newest hero, Kenny The Cat. // Attempting to get more work out of Squidward, Mr. Krabs spins the story of the monstrous Yeti Crab, which eats lazy workers.

10446.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10446.description: A rash of thefts in the Valley of Peace has the villagers in uproar and things only get worse when the culprit appears to be... Monkey?

10447.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10447.description: Po's Kung Fu hero, Kwan the Unkillable, comes to the Valley of Peace and appears to be a feeble old man. Po agrees to stage a fight to help him get back on top. But Kwan may not be as weak as he looks.

10448.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10448.description: As the zoo starts feeding them imitation fish cakes, the penguins take matters into their own flippers and hatch a plan to hijack a fish delivery truck. // During a particularly cold day, the rats show up and challenge the penguins to a hockey match.

10449.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10449.description: As the vet gathers the penguins to give them a shot, Skipper's fear of needles takes over and he goes on the run. // During a solar eclipse, Phil and Mason convince the bossy Julien that the sky spirits are angry at him. He starts acting extra-nice.

10450.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
10450.description: Aang and the kids finally arrive in Ba Sing Se to see the Earth King, only to find mysterious forces within the city conspiring to stop them. Meanwhile, Jet tries to find proof that Zuko and Uncle are Fire Nation.

10451.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
10451.description: A series of short stories, highlighting different characters and their individual adventures in the city. Tales of Katara and Toph, Uncle, Sokka, Aang, Zuko, and Momo.

10452.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10452.description: In order to save money, Mr. Krabs fires SpongeBob. Unable to just “do nothing”, SpongeBob decides to go back to work doing anything, anywhere.

10453.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10453.description: SpongeBob tries to take a shortcut to work, but becomes lost along the way. // After failing his driver’s test again, Mr. Krabs decides to teach SpongeBob how to drive himself.

10454.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10454.description: After receiving an invitation to a gallery opening, Squidward scrambles to find a friend to take with him. // While trying to order a special sandwich, Patrick gets swept up in the fast paced world of business.

10455.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
10455.description: The Turtles are accidentally transported to the past, and they cross paths with a familiar ninja clan.

10456.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
10456.description: Leo decides to sneak into Shredder's Lair alone only to face the biggest mutant threat yet.

10457.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10457.description: Master Chao visits the valley to oversee a Tournament. Shifu is convinced that Po and Master Chao want to replace him. Shifu's old enemy, Pai Mei, arrives in the middle of the tournament and threatens to destroy Shifu.

10458.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
10458.description: Master Yao returns to the Jade Palace and announces that he's offering the Valley of Peace a one-day 'Wonder and Wisdom Exchange'. Anyone who brings him a new wonder will be allowed to ask him a single question.

10459.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10459.description: Mort is exposed to Kowalski's super-ray, and he grows super-big and strong. // Marlene gets a new roommate! At first, she's excited to have a new best friend. But her attitude changes when her roommate turns out to have some pretty disgusting habits.

10460.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10460.description: The rats have been terrorizing Roger the alligator. He asks the penguins for help. Their solution: swap Roger's brain with Rico's, and let the but kicking begin! // A robot is sent to the zoo to learn the habits of lemurs before it's sent into space.

10461.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
10461.description: When the penguins bring Marlene with them on a sno-cone mission in the park, she can't handle the freedom of being outside the zoo walls. // Max the cat is on the run from evil animal control Officer X, and he comes to the penguins for help.

10462.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
10462.description: When SpongeBob cooks at home, Mr. Krabs' customers leave his restaurant and head for SpongeBob's Place. // When Plankton gets kicked out of the house, it's up to SpongeBob to teach him how to win his computer wife back.

16950.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
16950.description: When stray snails start appearing around Bikini Bottom, SpongeBob decides to care for them himself. // To defend Bikini Bottom’s honor, Patrick enters a Krabby Patty eating competition.
